INSERT INTO `page` VALUES ('36', '1', 'showdoc', '2', '1', '我的投标', '    \n**简要描述：** \n\n- 我的投标（参与中）接口\n\n**请求URL：** \n- ` /api/index/getMyBid `\n  \n**请求方式：**\n- POST \n\n**参数：** \n\n|参数名|必选|类型|说明|\n|:----    |:---|:----- |-----   |\n|appId |是  |string |   |\n|appSecret |是  |string |     |\n|uid     |是  |int | 用户id    |\n\n **返回示例**\n\n``` \n  {\n    &quot;code&quot;: 200,\n    &quot;data&quot;: [ //无数据时返回空\n        {\n			&quot;id&quot; : 105,\n            &quot;borrow_id&quot;: 28,	\n            &quot;uid&quot;: 22,	//用户uid\n            &quot;borrow_funds&quot;: 1000.000,		//投资金额\n            &quot;plan_title&quot;: &quot;28期&quot;,	//计划名称\n            &quot;rate&quot;: 6.00,		//利率\n            &quot;profit&quot;: 32.5,		//收益\n			&quot;recive_money&quot; : 768.56, //已获利息\n            &quot;begin_time&quot;: &quot;2016-03-15&quot;, //计息开始时间(未计算时为0)\n            &quot;end_time&quot;: &quot;2017-03-16&quot;,	//计息结束时间(未计算时为0);\n            &quot;status&quot;: &quot;计息中&quot;,		//状态\n            &quot;total_number&quot;: 2	//参与人数\n        },\n        {\n			&quot;id&quot; : 106,\n            &quot;borrow_id&quot;: 28,\n            &quot;uid&quot;: 22,\n            &quot;borrow_funds&quot;: 500.000,\n            &quot;plan_title&quot;: &quot;28期&quot;,\n            &quot;rate&quot;: 6.00,\n            &quot;profit&quot;: 16.25,\n			&quot;recive_money&quot; : 768.56, //已获利息\n            &quot;begin_time&quot;: &quot;2016-03-15&quot;,\n            &quot;end_time&quot;: &quot;2017-03-16&quot;,\n            &quot;status&quot;: &quot;计息中&quot;,\n            &quot;total_number&quot;: 2\n        }\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n **返回参数说明** \n\n|参数名|类型|说明|\n|:-----  |:-----|-----                           |\n|id |int   |即是bcid(获取详情需要)  |\n|borrow_id |int   |散标id  |\n|uid |int   |用户uid  |\n|borrow_funds |decimal   |投资金额  |\n|plan_title |string   |计划名称  |\n|rate |decimal   |年利率  |\n|profit |decimal   |收益  |\n|recive_money| decimal |已获利息 |\n|begin_time |string   |计息开始时间(未计算时为0)  |\n|end_time |string   |计息结束时间(未计算时为0)  |\n|status |string   |状态  |\n|total_number |int   |参与人数  |\n\n **备注** \n```\n- 错误码：\n		1001 令牌验证失败，\n		1002 uid不存在\n```\n\n', '99', '1459396241');
