INSERT INTO `page_history` VALUES ('84', '32', '1', 'showdoc', '2', '1', '散标详情', '    \n**简要描述：** \n\n- 散标详情接口\n\n**请求URL：** \n- ` /api/index/getLoanDetail `\n  \n**请求方式：**\n- POST \n\n**参数：** \n\n|参数名|必选|类型|说明|\n|:----    |:---|:----- |-----   |\n|appId |是  |string |用户名   |\n|appSecret |是  |string | 密码    |\n|bid     |是  |int | 散标id(即是bid)    |\n|uid     |否  |int | 用户组id    |\n\n **返回示例**\n\n``` \n  {\n    &quot;code&quot;: 200,\n    &quot;data&quot;: {\n        &quot;title&quot;: &quot;1111&quot;,	//标题\n        &quot;real_name&quot;: &quot;&quot;,	//真实姓名\n        &quot;upload_info&quot; : &quot;&quot;, //上传资料图片，存储路径(暂时无用)\n        &quot;pay_back_type&quot;: &quot;等额本金&quot;,	//还款方式(1.等额本金  2.等额本息  3.还本付息)\n        &quot;is_late&quot; : &quot;已结束&quot;,   //是否到期\n        &quot;deadline&quot; : &quot;1458461518&quot;,	//该标的截止时间戳\n\n        &quot;borrow_funds&quot;: 80000,	//借款金额\n        &quot;rate&quot;: 6.00,	//年利率/日利率\n        &quot;time_value&quot;: 12,		//借款时间期限\n        &quot;time_type&quot; : 1,	//借款时间期限类型（1按月，2按天）\n        &quot;type&quot;: &quot;质押标&quot;,	//发标的类型（1质押标，2抵押标）\n        &quot;gender&quot;: &quot;男&quot;,	//用户性别\n        &quot;birthday&quot;: &quot;01-01&quot;,	//生日\n        &quot;marriage&quot;: &quot;0&quot;,	//是否已经结婚（0未结婚，1已结婚）\n        &quot;education&quot;: &quot;0&quot;,	//教育程度\n        &quot;hashouse&quot; : &quot;0&quot;,	//是否有房子\n        &quot;national&quot;: &quot;0&quot;,	//籍贯\n        &quot;content&quot;: &quot;468465&quot;,	//详细说明\n        &quot;industry&quot;: &quot;&quot;,		//工作所属行业\n        &quot;native_place&quot;: &quot;&quot;,		//现住址\n        &quot;monthly_income&quot;: 0,	//月收入\n        &quot;borrow_record&quot;: 10,	//借款记录\n        &quot;success_count&quot;: 9,	//成功借款\n        &quot;auctions_count&quot;: 1,	//流标\n        &quot;unpaid_count&quot;: 0,	//待还期数\n        &quot;paid_count&quot;: 0,		//成功还款\n        &quot;overdue_pay&quot;: 0,		//逾期还清\n        &quot;late_not&quot;: 0, 			//逾期未还\n    	&quot;refunds_list&quot;: [\n  